(145, 0, '2023-07-26 10:21:31', '2023-07-26 10:21:31', 'Hey there! ecohub.live \r\n \r\nDid you know that it is possible to send message wholly legit and fully? We present a legitimate new method of sending requests through contact forms. You can locate these feedback forms on lots of websites. \r\nWhen such business offers are sent, no personal data is employed, and messages are dispatched to forms specifically created to securely and safely receive messages and appeals. Messages sent through Communication Forms have less of a chance of being classified as spam, as they are viewed as important. \r\nYou have the chance to use our service without having to pay anything. \r\nYou can trust us to send up to 50,000 messages. \r\n \r\nThe cost of sending one million messages is $59. \r\n \r\nThis message was automatically generated. \r\nPlease use the contact details below to get in touch with us. \r\n \r\nContact us. \r\nTelegram - https://t.me/FeedbackFormEU \r\nSkype  live:feedbackform2019 \r\nWhatsApp  +375259112693 \r\nWhatsApp  https://wa.me/+375259112693 \r\n \r\nWe only use chat for communication.', 'We guarantee the successful delivery of your emails.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'we-guarantee-the-successful-delivery-of-your-emails', '', '', '2023-07-26 10:21:31', '2023-07-26 10:21:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost/eco/we-guarantee-the-successful-delivery-of-your-emails/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
