(150, 0, '2023-09-02 22:48:44', '2023-09-02 22:48:44', 'Howdy-ho! ecohub.live \r\n \r\nDid you know that it is possible to send proposal fully legal? We sell a way of sending letters through contact forms to deliver an unique and ersonalized message. These feedback forms can be spotted on a plethora of webpages. \r\nWhen such business proposals are sent, no personal data is used, and messages are securely sent to forms specifically designed to receive them. Feedback Forms make sure that messages won\'t be seen as junk, as they are considered essential. \r\nWe give you a chance to experience our service for free. \r\nWe can deliver up to 50,000 messages on your instruction. \r\n \r\nThe cost of sending one million messages is $59. \r\n \r\nThis message was automatically generated. \r\nPlease use the contact details below to get in touch with us. \r\n \r\nContact us. \r\nTelegram - https://t.me/FeedbackFormEU \r\nSkype  live:contactform_18 \r\nWhatsApp - +375259112693 \r\nWhatsApp  https://wa.me/+375259112693 \r\nWe only use chat for communication.', 'Giving feedback through the feedback form.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'giving-feedback-through-the-feedback-form', '', '', '2023-09-02 22:48:44', '2023-09-02 22:48:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/eco/giving-feedback-through-the-feedback-form/', 0, 'post', '', 3),
